WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.340
Also help out by recycling and reusing things when you can.

00:00:03.590 --> 00:00:05.900
Rather than throwing out all your gadgets and gizmos,

00:00:05.900 --> 00:00:10.150
see if you can find another use for them or donate them to charity if the product is still good.

00:00:10.230 --> 00:00:15.080
Recycling helps fight climate change because it takes less energy to make something from recycled products 

00:00:15.080 --> 00:00:16.350
than starting from scratch.

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:16.900
Also,

00:00:16.900 --> 00:00:21.660
consider buying things with less packaging in the first place or items that use recyclable package.

00:00:16.900 --> 00:00:21.660
